quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  67,27,"Nde …ďe yi'oyta (lette) …óen ka …ďadii, geece yeddu…ďe …ďen suni geece heefer…ďe, […ďe] wi'anee : \"Ko …óum …óoo woni ko …óa…ď…ďayno…óon"
  67,28,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, si Allah ∆īettitii lam min e wonndii…ďe am maa O yurmaama men, ko hommbo da…óndata heefer…ďe …ďen lette muusu…óe"
  67,29,"Maaku : \"Ko Kanko Jom hinaraŇčke On. Men gom…óinii Mo, ko e Makko kadi men fawii. Aray nde anndon ko hommbo woni e majjere …ďanngunde"
  67,30,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, si ndiyam mon …óam wattinii …ďee…ďu…óam, ko hommbo addanta on ndiyam ilay…óam"
  68,1,Nuun. Mi woondirii karambol e ko …ďe winndirta kon
  68,2,"Aan a wonaa, sabu neema Joomi maa on, haangaa…óo"
  68,3,"Ko pellet, hino woodan-maa njo…ďdi ndi ta∆īondirtaa"
  68,4,"E ko pellet, hi…óa e jikku mawngu"
  68,5,"Aray nde tinaa, …ďe yi'a kam…ďe kadi"
  68,6,ko hommbo e mo'on woni haangaa…óo on
  68,7,"Pellet, ko Joomi maa …ďuri anndude majju…óo on laawol Makko ngol, ko Kanko kadi …ďuri anndude feewu…ďe …ďen"
  68,8,Wata a tewto fennoo…ďe …ďen
  68,9,"Hi…ďe yi…ói si a newantono (…ďe), …ďe newano-(maa)"
  68,10,"Wata a tewto kadi kala …óuu…óu…óo woondugol, hoy…óo"
  68,11,"…óuu…óu…óo nyo*ugol, …óuu…óu…óo yaarugol baddi"
  68,12,"…óuu…óu…óo ha…óugol mo∆ī∆īere, jaggitoowo, bakkondin…óo"
  68,13,"yoora-…ďerndeejo e hoore …óum, he…ďiraa…óo nii"
  68,14,fii o wonii jom jawdi e …ďi…ó…ďe
  68,15,"Si Aayeeje Amen …óen janngaama e [tawnde] makko, o wi'a: \"Ko tinndi adinoo…ďe"
